# Earth Pulse — optional environment variables
# Copy to `.env` and fill in. All are OPTIONAL; the app runs fully without them.

# Global live ships (aisstream.io WebSocket AIS).
# Without this key the ship layer uses the keyless Fintraffic Baltic feed.
# With it, ships go WORLDWIDE.
#   1. Sign in at https://aisstream.io and create a free API key.
#   2. Put it here (and add the same var in the Vercel project settings).
#   3. Rebuild.
# NOTE: this is a client-side WebSocket, so the key ends up in the browser
# bundle — use a FREE, disposable key, never a paid/secret one.
VITE_AISSTREAM_KEY=
